title: 服务端更换地图然后启动报错
txt_content:
[10:19:34] [Server thread/INFO]: Preparing level "world"
[10:19:34] [Server thread/INFO]: This world was saved with mod mcp version 9.05 and it is now at version 9.42, things may not work well
[10:19:34] [Server thread/ERROR]: This world was saved with mod Forge which appears to be missing, things may not work well
[10:19:34] [Server thread/ERROR]: This world was saved with mod InputFix which appears to be missing, things may not work well
[10:19:34] [Server thread/ERROR]: This world was saved with mod worldedit which appears to be missing, things may not work well
[10:19:34] [Server thread/INFO]: Injecting existing registry data into this server instance
[10:19:34] [Server thread/WARN]: Forge Mod Loader detected missing/unknown registrie(s).

There are 3 missing registries in this save.
If you continue the missing registries will get removed.
This may cause issues, it is advised that you create a world backup before continuing.

Missing Registries:
fml:blocks
fml:items
fmlgr:villagerprofessions


Run the command /fml confirm or or /fml cancel to proceed.
Alternatively start the server with -Dfml.queryResult=confirm or -Dfml.queryResult=cancel to preselect the answer.
>




1.12的catserve服务端，更换了个主世界的地图就这样报错了
上次弄这个猫端换和这次一样的地图就没出错
我用多世界插件加了个世界
然后换这个世界的地图还是报错

replies.txt_content:

replies.txt_content:
1832701651 发表于 2020-7-31 10:26
啥原因啊报这种错误
你换的地图里面有些mod物品
然后你目前服务器没有安装这些mod
所以出问题了
不用管就行

replies.author: 454564啊
replies.txt_content: 你应该是删除了mod，/fml confirm就可以继续开起来了
